</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Times\" title=\"The Times\">The Times</a></i> obituary, 30 May 1941, p. 7</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>The Times</i>, obituary of Hugh Wontner, 27 November 1992</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>The Times</i> obituary gives his age as 86, but does not cite date of birth, and the dates and age given in the <i>Oxford Dictionary of National Biography</i> have been used above.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1261\nCached time: 20180910002957\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.096 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.116 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 241/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 721/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 83/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 3885/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 1/400\nLua time usage: 0.028/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   78.381      1 -total\n 65.34%   51.214      1 Template:Reflist\n 44.11%   34.572      1 Template:Webarchive\n 34.53%   27.067      1 Template:Authority_control\n  3.24%    2.537      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:24397796-0!canonical and timestamp 20180910002956 and revision id 838787180\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","hidden":"","*":"Webarchive_template_wayback_links"},{"sortkey":"Reeves-Smith, George","*":"People_associated_with_Gilbert_and_Sullivan"},{"sortkey":"Reeves-Smith, George"